parts.args:
{"title":"fix: Correct REQUIRED_API_BASE env var in vigil-app Deployment","body":"Root cause: The REQUIRED_API_BASE environment variable was set to an empty string in the Deployment manifest, causing nginx to generate an invalid proxy_pass directive in the configuration template.

Evidence: Nginx logs show "invalid number of arguments in \"proxy_pass\" directive" error. Both live and declared YAML show REQUIRED_API_BASE: value: ''.

Fix: Updated the REQUIRED_API_BASE environment variable to a valid URL 'http://app-backend' to prevent nginx configuration errors."}
